    "DBP's initial large decrease in loss is done in almost half the time as BP, maintaining the efficiency gain despite the additional compute.",
    "Figure 4 shows the downstream task performance using pre-trained DBP-MAE and BP-MAE.",
    "Here too, we observe clear visual differences when comparing the performance between the two regimes of semantic segmentation fine-tuning on ADE20K.",
